text: Zoltán Jelenffy (26 October 1876 - 21 January 1924) was a Hungarian sports shooter. He competed in four events at the 1912 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1876 births Category:1924 deaths Category:Hungarian male sport shooters Category:Olympic shooters of Hungary Category:Shooters at the 1912 Summer Olympics Category:People from Sighetu Marmației
